{"type":"route","meta":{"status":200,"headers":{"content-type":"text/markdown","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/[[...slug]]/layout,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/[[...slug]]/route,_N_T_/llms.mdx/docs/clients/content.md"}},"body":"# Clients (/docs/clients)\n\n\n\nThe Client List is your salon's client database. Every person who visits your salon can have a profile here, making it easy to look them up, track their history, and manage their memberships and vouchers.\n\nClick **Clients** in the left menu to get started.\n\n***\n\nThe client list [#the-client-list]\n\nThe main view shows a table of all your clients with the following columns:\n\n| Column        | What it shows                              |\n| ------------- | ------------------------------------------ |\n| Client name   | Name with an avatar (initials if no photo) |\n| Mobile number | Their phone number                         |\n| Reviews       | Internal reviews added by your team        |\n| Sales         | Total amount spent across all visits       |\n| Created at    | When the client was added to the system    |\n\nUse the **search bar** at the top to find anyone by name, email, or phone number.\n\nThe list is paginated — use the **Previous / Next** buttons at the bottom to navigate, and adjust the **Show** dropdown to control how many results appear per page.\n\n***\n\nAdding a new client [#adding-a-new-client]\n\n<Steps>\n  <Step>\n    Click the **+ Add** button in the top right corner. A form will pop up.\n  </Step>\n\n  <Step>\n    Fill in the client's details:\n\n    * **First Name** (required)\n    * **Last Name**\n    * **Phone Number** (required — select the country code from the dropdown)\n    * **Email**\n    * **Date of Birth**\n    * **Notes** — any internal notes about the client\n    * **Location** — assign them to a specific branch\n  </Step>\n\n  <Step>\n    Click **Save Client**. They'll appear in the list and be available for booking straight away.\n  </Step>\n</Steps>\n\n<Callout type=\"tip\">\n  You can also add a client on the spot while booking an appointment in the Calendar — no need to come here first.\n</Callout>\n\n***\n\nViewing a client's profile [#viewing-a-clients-profile]\n\nClick on any client's name to open their full profile in a panel. The profile has three sections:\n\n**Left — Client details**\n\n* Name, phone, and email\n* **Edit client** — update any of their details\n* **Add review** — leave an internal note or review about this client\n* Date of birth (can be added here if not set)\n* Date the client was added to the system\n\n**Middle — Navigation tabs**\nSwitch between different parts of the client's history:\n\n| Tab          | What it shows                                                  |\n| ------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Appointments | All appointments with status (Paid, Scheduled, No Show, etc.)  |\n| Sales        | All completed sales with service name, total, and View Details |\n| Products     | Products purchased by this client                              |\n| Vouchers     | Vouchers linked to this client                                 |\n| Memberships  | Active and completed membership packages with session counts   |\n| Loyalty      | Loyalty programme activity                                     |\n\n**Right — Detail view**\nClicking any item in the tabs shows the full detail. For example, clicking a sale opens the VAT invoice with the service, staff, subtotal, VAT, and total — with options to print or void the sale.\n\n***\n\nQuick reference [#quick-reference]\n\n| Feature         | Details                                                           |\n| --------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Search          | By name, email, or phone                                          |\n| Add client form | First name, phone required — email, DOB, notes, location optional |\n| Sales total     | Shown directly in the client list                                 |\n| Full profile    | Appointments, Sales, Products, Vouchers, Memberships, Loyalty     |\n| Quick add       | Create a client directly from the Calendar while booking          |\n"}